4) Return a compact table of top 20 groups ordered by exceed_count_window descending. Include columns: cmdb_id, kpi_name, total_points, global_p95, points_in_window, exceed_count_window, first_exceed_timestamp. If multiple groups have the same exceed_count_window, order by first_exceed_timestamp ascending. Keep output bounded to these columns and <=20 rows.
